{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)draggable","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L261"},"title":"draggable","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"draggable","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getter","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"=","kind":"text"},{"text":"isDraggable","kind":"identifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"draggable","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If this property is set to "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the user can drag the annotation after"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pressing and holding the view, and the associated annotation object must also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implement the "},{"code":"setCoordinate:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method. The default value of this property is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" lets the map view know that the annotation is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"always draggable. In other words, you cannot conditionalize drag operations by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attempting to stop an operation that has already been initiated; doing so can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"lead to undefined behavior. Once begun, the drag operation should always"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"continue to completion."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Enable users to drag ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" objects on your map.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/draggable":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"draggable","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable."}],"fragments":[{"text":"draggable","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview"}}}